  "detailed_description": "Using the mechanism on the wall, the protagonist has activated many doors inside the complex. Behind one of these doors is a special chicken that needs help finding its way out. Make your way through the maze of puzzles and try to save the chicken's life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066660/extras/f4f1d0712fb50d6ea9b5b65754d7f490.poster.avif?t=1772992259\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066660/extras/f4f1d0712fb50d6ea9b5b65754d7f490.webm?t=1772992259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3066660/extras/f4f1d0712fb50d6ea9b5b65754d7f490.mp4?t=1772992259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A great classic puzzle game in a new form!<br></li><li> A mix of horror and Sokoban? Why not!<br></li><li> Chickens. Again!<br></li><li> Retro-styled graphics.</li></ul><br><i>If you need a little hint, check out the news about the game's release.</i>",
